title: GE Monogram 30 Professional Stainless Steel French Door Wall Oven ZET1FHSS Overview
description:

10-Pass Bake Element. 10-Pass Dual Broil Element. Closed Door Broiling
Oven Rack Features 
3 Self-Clean Heavy-Duty Full Extension Oven Racks. 6 Ladder-Rack Positions
Interior Oven Light 
2 Theater-Style LED Light Columns

Cooking Technology Convection

True European Convection with Direct Air. Reverse Air Convection. Flat Back Convection Cover
Configuration 
Single Oven
Control Type 
Electronic Dial. Backlit LCD Display. Brillion™ - Enabled. Backlit Digital Knobs

Oven Cooking Modes
Convection Bake. Convection Bake Multi-Rack. Convection Roast. Convection Broil. Thermal Bake. Thermal Broil
Broiler Pan and Grid- Yes
Self-Clean Oven Door Lock Automatic
Oven Interior
Midnight Blue. True Hidden Bake Element
Cleaning Time Variable with Delay Clean Option
